@everyone  We've had some questions about working at Meta so @Ultra Instinct and myself would like to offer the community an opportunity to ask about the culture, compensation structure, benefits, performance management or anything else you'd like to know. 
Please thumbs up if you'e interested in joining this session and feel free to post some questions you'd like to get answered on this channel. 
We can target Friday Jan 21st for this chat.

@everyone  Thank you to all those that could join today's chat!  🙏   It was a great watercooler style chat with awesome participation from the group.  I'd love if you could take a minute to share your feedback so we can keep evolving and improving, and if you're interested in co-hosting a future session, please let me know.  Have a great weekend!  
**__Feedback survey:__**
https://forms.gle/1mcqEgMQMWinEybC6

@here

The next event will be on Nov 1st at 1 pm PT. 
Stephanie Chu, Sr Dir of TPM at LinkedIn will be joining us. 
@paytun will share a slido next week for you to contribute your questions. Stephanie is a very accomplished leader and will have a lot of insights into the TPM tradecraft
